Pirate Adventure (BYTE magazine)

Scott Adams Classic Adventures #2
(c) 1978-1984 Scott Adams/Adventure International

Only by exploring this strange island will you be able to uncover the clues necessary to lead you to your elusive goal -- recovering the lost treasures of Long John Silver.

This adventure is a lightly edited version of that published in Level II BASIC for the TRS-80 in BYTE Magazine Volume 05 Number 12 - December 1980.

Difficulty Level: Beginner
